Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:11.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:12.86,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:16.01,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Being late for watch duty \Nmakes trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:16.59,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:18.86,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Today's menu, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.37,sign_513_9_Beef_Trash,,0000,0000,0000,,Food Waste
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:23.37,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"Leftover special."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:25.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's too honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:28.25,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,At times like these, \Nwe go with you-know-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.25,sign_678_13_Today_s_Menu,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Menu
